title: Mommy, Why is there a Server in the House? (Microsoft Book)
description:
Mommy, Why is there a Server in the House?
is a children's book published by Microsoft as part of their (from 2007, by now defunct) advertising campaign "Stay at Home Servers". Windows Home Server and all that...

"Helping your child understand the stay-at-home server"
